  <Docs>
    <summary>Holds options for creating XPS documents with <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.SKDocument" />.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKDocumentXpsOptions` holds configuration options for creating XPS documents
via <xref:SkiaSharp.SKDocument>.

Set the desired properties and pass the struct to
`SKDocument.CreateXps` when opening a document.

## Examples

```csharp
var options = new SKDocumentXpsOptions
{
    Dpi = 300,
    AllowNoPngs = false,
};

using var stream = File.Create("output.xps");
using var document = SKDocument.CreateXps(stream, options);
using var canvas = document.BeginPage(595, 842);
// draw on canvas...
document.EndPage();
document.Close();
```
]]></format></remarks>
